    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Portable slabs or flat surfaces used for throwing or hand-building clay objects, or supporting works in a kiln; may be attachments to potter's wheels.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
